<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
    .header { background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0; }
    .content { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 20px; border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px; }
    .credentials { background-color: #fff; border: 2px solid #4CAF50; border-radius: 5px; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .login-button { display: inline-block; background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; }
    .warning { background-color: #fff3cd; border: 1px solid #ffeaa7; border-radius: 5px; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>üéâ Welcome to Utah ABA Finder!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Congratulations, <%= @registration.provider_name %>!</h2>
      
      <p>Your provider registration has been <strong>approved</strong> and your account is now active. You can now log in to manage your provider profile and connect with families seeking ABA services.</p>
      
      <div class="credentials">
        <h3>üîê Your Login Credentials</h3>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= @user.email %></p>
        <p><strong>Password:</strong> <code style="background: #f0f0f0; padding: 5px; border-radius: 3px;"><%= @password %></code></p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="warning">
        <p><strong>‚ö†Ô∏è Important:</strong> Please save these credentials securely. You can change your password after your first login.</p>
      </div>
      
      <p><strong>Next Steps:</strong></p>
      <ol>
        <li>Log in using the credentials above</li>
        <li>Complete your provider profile</li>
        <li>Add your service locations and details</li>
        <li>Start receiving inquiries from families</li>
      </ol>
      
      <a href="<%= ENV['FRONTEND_URL'] || 'https://utah-aba-finder.com' %>/login" class="login-button">Login Now</a>
      
      <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
      
      <p>Welcome aboard!</p>
      <p><em>The Utah ABA Finder Team</em></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
